OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FThames Water shareholders  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Frefuse to inject more cash 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Thames Water's shareholders are        
OL,6, refusing to give the struggling water  
OL,7, giant extra cash unless bills rise.    
OL,9,FThey were due to invest #500m by the   
OL,10,Fend of March, but have withheld it     
OL,11,Fsaying the company's turnaround plan is
OL,12,F"uninvestible".                        
OL,14,FShareholders want the regulator Ofwat  
OL,15,Fto agree to a substantial increase in  
OL,16,Fwater bills for Thames' customers over 
OL,17,Fthe next five years.                   
OL,19,FFears emerged last year that Thames    
OL,20,Fcould collapse due to its huge debts.  
